last_episode_to_air.name: Under Construction
last_episode_to_air.overview: When presented with differing opportunities, Shawna and Mia must decide once and for all whether their loyalties lie with Francois or Chastity; Maurice and Shawna face the music, as Mia gets a disconcerting wake-up call at Melissa's birthday party.

name: Rap Sh!t
overview: Two estranged high school friends from Miami reunite to form a rap group.

episodes.name: Something for The City
episodes.overview: Stuck at a dead-end hotel job while her long-distance boyfriend attends law school, aspiring rapper Shawna spontaneously invites her estranged friend Mia out for drinks – yielding surprising results.

episodes.name: Something for The Girls
episodes.overview: After their first video gains traction, Shawna and Mia’s second attempt at success leads to creative differences.

episodes.name: Something for The Hood
episodes.overview: As the duo get more serious about their music, Shawna dives deeper into a scheme to help cover costs. Meanwhile, Mia fields a proposal from her promoter friend Chastity.

episodes.name: Something for The Clubs
episodes.overview: Shawna’s boyfriend Cliff criticizes the pair’s latest work, while Chastity attempts to convince a club to play their song.

episodes.name: Something for The Weekend
episodes.overview: The girls take a trip to New York where Shawna finally reunites with Cliff and Mia meets up with a wealthy stranger.

episodes.name: Something for The Gram
episodes.overview: After the events in New York, Mia deals with hateful comments and trolls while Lamont has to step up. Meanwhile, Shawna decides to ditch work for the day.

episodes.name: Something for The DJ
episodes.overview: Before heading to her first-ever live performance, Shawna faces off against a former friend, whose critical words about the pair’s lack of direction hit home.

episodes.name: Something for The Road
episodes.overview: After the show, Mia and Shawna find themselves questioning the group’s future. Later, Mia forms an unexpected connection, while Shawna considers an offer.

episodes.name: Yield
episodes.overview: Before their upcoming tour with Reina Reign, Shawna reconnects with Francois, while Mia hesitates over leaving Melissa behind.

episodes.name: Heavy Traffic
episodes.overview: While struggling to see eye-to-eye on tour, Shawna and Mia find themselves at an uncomfortable afterparty.

episodes.name: Rough Road
episodes.overview: As Mia enjoys her time with a love interest, Chastity and Shawna get real, and Maurice receives an ultimatum.

episodes.name: Detour
episodes.overview: Interestingly frustrated with Francois and Reina Reign’s behavior, Shawna, Mia and Chastity start to push back. Later, Shawna bonds with Lord AK in the studio, while Mia frets over her mistake with Ca$h.

episodes.name: Dead End
episodes.overview: In Los Angeles, Francois entices Shawna and Mia with lucrative deal -- but only under one condition. At the Billboard party, Mia balances two love interests, Shawna and Lord AK draw closer together, and Chastity starts to lose her confidence.

episodes.name: U-Turn
episodes.overview: After returning to Miami, Shawna meets up with Maurice, and Mia finds that her old life has changed without her.

episodes.name: No Parking
episodes.overview: With their tour officially over, Shawna weighs a career-changing offer from Francois, while Chastity reaches back out to an A&R rep. As Mia focuses on her family, a discovery threatens her relationship with Lamont.

episodes.name: Under Construction
episodes.overview: When presented with differing opportunities, Shawna and Mia must decide once and for all whether their loyalties lie with Francois or Chastity; Maurice and Shawna face the music, as Mia gets a disconcerting wake-up call at Melissa's birthday party.
